ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Newfoundland and Labrador 1) The Hon. David Orsborn - February 6-7, 2012 and February 28 to March 1, 2012 and 2) The Hon. B. Gale Welsh - March 14-31, 2012
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of Newfoundland and Labrador (1) the Hon. DAVID B. ORSBORN from February 6-7, 2012, inclusive, and from February 28 to March 1, 2012, inclusive; and (2) the Hon. B. GALE WELSH from March 14 to 31, 2012, inclusive.
